Key Match Events: South Africa defeated Pakistan by one wicket in a nail-biting contest.
Aiden Markram scored a brilliant 91 off 93 balls with 7 fours and 3 sixes.
Shaheen Afridi provided crucial breakthroughs to reduce South Africa to 250 for eight.
The last-wicket duo of Keshav Maharaj and Tabraiz Shamsi saw South Africa home.
